19\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Isoc.\">Isoc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12.19</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">νικᾶν . . πανταχοῦ . . ἔφυν π. εἰτ σέ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg006.perseus-grc1:1053\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ph.\">Ph.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1053</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πᾶς</foreign> is sts. omitted, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">θνῄσκουσι [πάντες] π. εἷς τις</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg004.perseus-grc1:118\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ OT\">OT</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">118</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀλλ᾽ ἔστι [πᾶσι] πλὴν σοί</foreign> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg004.perseus-grc1:370\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">370</biblScope> </bibl>): freq. with <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἄλλος</foreign> (much <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">like</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">ἤ</ref> </xr>)<cit TEIform=\"cit\"><quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">, τί οὖν μ᾽ ἄνωγας ἄλλο π. ψευδῆ λέγειν;</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg006.perseus-grc1:100\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ph.\">Ph.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">100</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greek